import React, {FC} from 'react'
import {Body, MainHero, MainTitle, SecondaryTitle} from './App.styles'

const App: FC = props => (
  <Body>
    <MainHero>
      <MainTitle>Knoa ROI Calculator</MainTitle>
      <SecondaryTitle>
        Input the number of employees to calculate the business impact Knoa UEM
        can have on your organization.
      </SecondaryTitle>
    </MainHero>
  </Body>
)

export default App
